{
  "stem": "1975.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He used to come to collect the rent and so forth and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we-- And he, truthfully-- I mean, our-- our life was-- our destiny was in his hands.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he would warn us and tell us when we can go out and get something to-- buy something to-- for-- to eat, or when we should stay away.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came in, I would say, about a week after-- a week or 10 days after the war started.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came in, very-- first of all, they took many, many prisoners, POWs, a tremendous amount, because their tactic was they-- they surrounded-- amazingly, they came from the north, rather than from the-- from the-- from the south or the west, southwest.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came up to Kaunas because they they had their system, the-- to encircle, and then to squeeze.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] And this is basically what they have done.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came in with-- with their motorcycles and with their armor, and nicely polished shoes, you know, boots.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and you can-- right away, we-- we were able to feel the-- the-- the German presence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they-- they were very regulated and very orderly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, everything had to be to the-- I mean, properly done.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was-- although they were very bad in in many aspects, but at least they had a certain authority, even more with the Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would let them function, but they-- they-- they had impressed upon them and the Lithuanians felt that there is a a power above them, that they just cannot do anything what they want.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, related to Jews, I mean, the-- the Germans would turn their head, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
